02:02.560 --> 02:05.680
<b>No doubt about it. You even smell like Tatsumi.</b>

02:05.680 --> 02:07.140
<b>It's really you.</b>

02:07.140 --> 02:08.690
<b>How dare you run away?</b>

02:08.690 --> 02:09.770
<b>I was so lonely.</b>

02:09.770 --> 02:11.900
<b>Wh-Why are you here?</b>

02:11.900 --> 02:16.070
<b>I've been on pest control for the Danger Beasts that are menacing the capital.</b>

02:16.650 --> 02:18.950
<b>What are <i>you</i> doing here?</b>

02:20.490 --> 02:21.620
<b><i>She's suspicious of me.</i></b>

02:22.280 --> 02:24.490
<b><i>If I don't answer carefully, I'm in deep trouble.</i></b>

02:25.830 --> 02:29.830
<b>Uh, before I answer, could you let me go?</b>

02:29.830 --> 02:31.130
<b>No.</b>

02:31.130 --> 02:33.880
<b>I can't think clearly with you this close to me.</b>

02:33.880 --> 02:35.210
<b>I won't let you run again.</b>

02:36.460 --> 02:38.760
<b>I-I'm training!</b>

02:38.760 --> 02:41.220
<b>They say a lot of Danger Beasts roam around here, you see.</b>

02:41.220 --> 02:43.350
<b>Then you're here to fight them too.</b>

02:43.350 --> 02:46.430
<b>Well? Have you joined the Revolutionary Army?</b>

02:47.810 --> 02:48.890
<b>Not yet.</b>

02:49.440 --> 02:51.770
<b>But I don't think I'll be changing my mind.</b>

02:52.270 --> 02:55.110
<b>I'm currently training to be a warrior.</b>

02:56.900 --> 02:58.490
<b>I see.</b>

02:58.490 --> 03:01.570
<b>Your physique has certainly become more pronounced.</b>

03:01.570 --> 03:02.870
<b>And you've clearly leveled up.</b>

03:03.830 --> 03:05.950
<b>You've done well in so short a time.</b>

03:05.950 --> 03:07.910
<b>I'm sure you'll continue to grow even stronger!</b>

03:07.910 --> 03:09.290
<b>W-Well...</b>

03:09.870 --> 03:12.290
<b><i>This isn't the time to let her sweet-talk me!</i></b>

03:12.710 --> 03:16.130
<b>The Danger Beasts here are pretty much wiped out.</b>

03:16.130 --> 03:18.090
<b>They were annoying, but...</b>

03:19.220 --> 03:21.430
<b>In a way, they led me to you.</b>

03:21.430 --> 03:23.390
<b>This can only be the work of fate.</b>

03:25.970 --> 03:28.730
<b>There's a surprising number of nuisances around here.</b>

03:29.140 --> 03:30.520
<b>You. The one who just hid.</b>

03:30.520 --> 03:32.770
<b>I know you're there. Come out.</b>

03:33.310 --> 03:35.690
<b>If you do not, I will strike with no further hesitation.</b>

03:38.650 --> 03:42.070
<b>Not bad. I thought I'd hidden pretty well.</b>

03:42.070 --> 03:45.990
<b>They don't call you the empire's strongest for nothing.</b>

03:45.990 --> 03:49.160
<b>I didn't think I'd run into you out here, though.</b>

03:49.160 --> 03:52.330
<b>I guess playtime's over.</b>

03:52.960 --> 03:56.840
<b>Sounds like you know why 
the Danger Beasts are loose.</b>

03:56.840 --> 03:58.920
<b>Allow me to escort you to the torture room.</b>

03:58.920 --> 04:01.970
<b>Sorry, but that's not my kind of thing.</b>

04:01.970 --> 04:06.350
<b>How about you take care of a few big toys of mine?{l-lewd (I have no video context. :c)}</b>

04:06.760 --> 04:08.260
<b>Imperial Relic Shambhala!{oh it's him}</b>

04:08.260 --> 04:09.100
<b>Activate!</b>

04:13.640 --> 04:15.100
<b>Wh-What's happening?</b>

04:22.360 --> 04:23.740
<b>Now, then.</b>

04:23.740 --> 04:27.120
<b>Who shall I play with next?</b>

04:29.700 --> 04:30.790
<b>Wh...</b>

04:30.790 --> 04:33.290
<b>What the hell is this?</b>

04:34.040 --> 04:36.290
<b>E-Esdeath...</b>

04:36.290 --> 04:37.710
<b>Could you hurt me, please?</b>

04:38.210 --> 04:39.500
<b>Tatsumi...</b>

04:39.500 --> 04:41.710
<b>I didn't know you were into that.</b>

04:41.710 --> 04:44.470
<b>We really <i>are</i> meant for each other.</b>

04:44.470 --> 04:46.470
<b>That isn't what I meant!</b>

04:46.470 --> 04:49.560
<b>That guy could be causing us to hallucinate all of this!</b>

04:50.010 --> 04:53.850
<b>If so, a little pain might snap us out of it!</b>

04:53.850 --> 04:54.730
<b>All right.</b>

04:55.270 --> 04:56.230
<b>Here goes.</b>

05:03.570 --> 05:05.320
<b>It isn't an illusion.</b>

05:05.320 --> 05:07.370
<b>The sensations are too real.</b>

05:07.370 --> 05:09.450
<b>The smell of salt and the ocean breeze...</b>

05:09.450 --> 05:11.040
<b>Temperature and humidity.</b>

05:11.040 --> 05:13.330
<b>I'd say this is reality.</b>

05:13.330 --> 05:14.410
<b>Which means...</b>

05:14.410 --> 05:18.000
<b>The man we saw before might 
have used some kind of ability.</b>

05:18.000 --> 05:19.750
<b>Did he teleport us here?</b>

05:20.170 --> 05:21.920
<b>Is that really possible?</b>

05:22.880 --> 05:27.430
<b>Forty-eight powerful armaments known as 
Imperial Relics lie scattered across the empire.</b>

05:27.430 --> 05:31.010
<b>I've heard that some can manipulate space and time,</b>

05:31.010 --> 05:34.180
<b>using secret arts from a lost country.</b>

05:34.180 --> 05:36.270
<b>Really? That's incredible!</b>

05:36.440 --> 05:37.560
<b><i>But wait...</i></b>

05:38.100 --> 05:42.320
<b><i>Is that how Incursio appears out of thin air when I call for it?</i></b>

05:43.570 --> 05:47.530
<b><i>When I think about it that way, 
it really scares me for some reason.</i></b>

05:48.200 --> 05:51.990
<b><i>Manipulating space and time is a powerful ability.</i></b>

05:51.990 --> 05:54.620
<b><i>Whatever Relic he has, 
it's definitely among the strongest.</i></b>

05:55.330 --> 05:57.080
<b><i>Just who is he?</i></b>

05:57.080 --> 05:59.580
<b>For now, let's get the lay of the land.</b>

06:03.800 --> 06:05.880
<b>Ocean as far as the eye can see.</b>

06:06.550 --> 06:09.010
